key_findings: CP solutions found but ALL had overlaps due to simplified Manhattan distance constraints
Multi-start SA from perturbed baseline found no valid improvements
The baseline configurations are at strong local/global optima
bbox3 binary is incompatible with system (GLIBC_2.34 required)
notes: Tried constraint programming with OR-Tools CP-SAT solver and multi-start SA. CP found solutions but they all had overlaps because the simplified distance constraints don't accurately model tree polygon geometry. Multi-start SA with 10 restarts per N found no improvements. This confirms the baseline is at a strong optimum.
